Gitorious Merge Request Monitor
A simple IRC bot for reporting the status of Gitorious merge requests.

Author: Jon Nordby
License: GPLv3+

== Dependencies ==
Python 2.x
Twisted
feedparser Python module

== Usage ==
- Change values in monitor.py
- Run python monitor.py

